$AI Profile: FS1 RETAIL

#Command Briefing

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("At 0600 hours, the GTC Aethelgard—or what's left of it—re-ignited its engines and broke orbit. It is currently on a direct heading for the Sirius jump node.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("We have attempted to contact the ship, but the only response is a continuous loop of what sounds like the crew screaming in unison. High Command has declared the ship rogue.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("You are to intercept. Do not destroy the ship unless absolutely necessary. We need to capture it and find out how the Shivans took control of a Terran cruiser from the inside.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none


#Briefing
